e approves plan to issue NCDs worth ₹500 crore.\nThe issuance has an option to increase to ₹2,000 crore.","summary":"IIFL Finance approves plan to issue NCDs worth ₹500 crore.\nThe issuance has an option to increase to ₹2,000 crore.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-13T06:39:31","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"809737620440201472","title":"ICRA reaffirmed IIFL Finance Ltd's NCDs, Sub-Debt, and Bank Lines ratings at AA Negative.\nCRISIL assigned AA Stable to Rs.2,000 Cr NCDs and reaffirmed other ratings as Stable or A1.","summary":"ICRA reaffirmed IIFL Finance Ltd's NCDs, Sub-Debt, and Bank Lines ratings at AA Negative.\nCRISIL assigned AA Stable to Rs.2,000 Cr NCDs and reaffirmed other ratings as Stable or A1.","url":"https://sqst.in/shareMessage?msgId=809737620440201477","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-12T16:18:12","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"480952","title":"IIFL Finance confirmed interest payments on NCDs as per SEBI regulations.\nInterest of Rs. 26.3L and Rs. 162.2L was paid on 07-02-2026 for respective NCDs.","summary":"IIFL Finance confirmed interest payments on NCDs as per SEBI regulations.\nInterest of Rs. 26.3L and Rs. 162.2L was paid on 07-02-2026 for respective NCDs.","url":"https://www.bseindia.com/stockinfo/AnnPdfOpen.aspx?Pname=885ebaec-ad10-4b85-8394-934ba4b87f68.pdf","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-09T18:57:33","source":"BSE"},{"id":"463910","title":"Gold prices plunged 12% in the spot market, leading to up to 8% fall in shares of Muthoot Finance and IIFL Finance.\nManappuram Finance fell 2% to ₹278.7, while Muthoot Finance dropped 6.1% to ₹3,596 amid a global bullion sell-off.","summary":"Gold prices plunged 12% in the spot market, leading to up to 8% fall in shares of Muthoot Finance and IIFL Finance.\nManappuram Finance fell 2% to ₹278.7, while Muthoot Finance dropped 6.1% to ₹3,596 amid a global bullion sell-off.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/market/muthoot-manappuram-finance-shares-fall-after-gold-prices-extend-losses-ws-l-198